,Recommended,224920,30572488,Posted: 17 March,all,Legato Bluesummers,"For anyone having issues with this game on Windows 7, 8 or 10. Just run the game using Windows Compatibility Mode ""Windows XP (Pack 3)."" All of my glitches and game crashes ended the moment I did that.As for the gameplay, yes it true there is no mouse compatibility, but it works perfectly fine with the keyboard. The camera follows the same movement dynamics as if you were using the Playstation 1 controller. It can be a strange at first to get used to, but the initial keyboard layout is set up to be comfortable for a keyboard only play.The game itself is course absolutely amazing. The story, world layout and character voicing are true examples what made the original PS1 gaming era one of (if not) the greatest."
